data.description: Step into comfort and style at this delightful 3-bed, 2.5-bath home. Positioned near the 11th hole of a PGA qualifying course, it offers a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication. Inside, revel in a spacious living area, an updated kitchen with granite countertops, trendy black tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. The fenced backyard is a peaceful retreat for entertaining, while additional recent updates in 2021 include the roof, flooring, paint, bathrooms, and windows. Conveniently located near schools and amenities, this colonial-style residence seamlessly combines classic charm with modern luxury. Make this house your new home and embrace a lifestyle of elegance, comfort, and convenience!
